  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Goo Goo Grapplers is a chaotic 1v1 couch party brawler, mixing MOBA-style strategy with baby-powered mayhem. Grab a controller and smack down your friend face-to-face!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/c36954a0f6a8a107319e476839dfca1f.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/c36954a0f6a8a107319e476839dfca1f.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power up your baby how you want in the dynamic shop! Discover new ways to build through ability upgrades and powerful passives each match! Want to yank your opponent across the arena with the <i>Sticky Hand</i>? Go for it. Feel like dropping <i>Building Blocks</i> to trip them up? Why not! Whether you're launching <i>Bouncy Balls</i> or calling in explosive <i>RC cars</i>, every match is a new chance to outwit each other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/d2fb995a2df23e32d2f56a6213a26233.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/d2fb995a2df23e32d2f56a6213a26233.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Baby Step</i> into a battlefield where every toy offers a new strategy. Will you build the ultimate baby warrior before your opponent does?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/1e73ba149e09d028ee75883c0bef9d5f.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/1e73ba149e09d028ee75883c0bef9d5f.webm?t=1767822584\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/15a344d17bdf7b1376e9a30a4b606ef8.webp?t=1767822584\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MOBA mechanics -</strong> Push down lanes, win map objectives, bring down your opponent</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Buff your Baby -</strong> Combine abilities and passives into hundreds of unique builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bring it Back -</strong> Clutch it out during your Last Stand!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local Multiplayer -</strong> Smart split screen for intense close quarters combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple Maps -</strong> Battle it out on multi and single lane maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lab It Up -</strong> Experiment at your own pace in training mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Analog Controls -</strong> Precise twin stick aiming and movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play it your way -</strong> Whether you prefer keyboard & mouse or controllers, pick the setup that suits your style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original soundtrack! -</strong> Featuring bumping tracks from various artists</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/323e773f442fc15b92b6f553bc169620.apng?t=1767822584\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316660/extras/323e773f442fc15b92b6f553bc169620.poster.avif?t=1767822584\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=96 /></picture></span></p></li></ul>",
